subject: HerbSpiceTopping
description: This category includes a variety of flavorful additions that enhance the taste of pizzas through the use of aromatic plants and spices. These toppings can range from dried herbs like oregano and basil to fresh options such as parsley and cilantro, each contributing its unique essence to the overall flavor profile. When sprinkled or layered onto a pizza, these ingredients not only elevate the dish’s aroma but also add a fresh, vibrant taste that complements the other components.
